ActEnterprise Cape Breton Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of State (Atlantic Canada Opportunities Agency) of SONNY MacDOUGALL, of Glace Bay, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office for a term of three years, in the place of Gregory MacKenzie, whose term has expired.
